<p>CBC has reporters stationed in the following cities. Main cities are listed in bold, with the notation <i>(M)</i>.</p>
<ul>
<li><b><a href="Whitehorse,_Yukon" title="Whitehorse, Yukon">Whitehorse</a>, <a href="Yukon" title="Yukon">Yukon</a> (M)</b></li>
