<li>Jerusalem - <a href="../../w/index-title=Margaret_Evans_(journalist)&action=edit&redlink=1.php.html" class="new" title="Margaret Evans (journalist) (page does not exist)">Margaret Evans</a> / Derek Stoffel / <a href="Sa%C5%A1a_Petricic" title="Saša Petricic">Saša Petricic</a></li>
